==English==
===Etymology===
From French ''[[#French|joie de vivre]]'', literally ‘joy of living’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ʒwæ də vi:vrə/}} (French {{IPAchar|/ʒwa də vivʀ/}})

===Noun phrase===
'''[[joie]] [[de]] [[vivre]]'''

# [[enjoyment|Enjoyment]] of [[living]]; happiness, ebullience, zest for life.

